            Stig Bertilsson (m) Bertil Danielsson (m) Kjell Johansson (fp)
            Ylva Annerstedt (fp) Erik Holmkvist (m) Filip Fridolfsson (m)
            Sten Svensson (m) Arne Svensson (m)
          </p>
